{
  "chapter": 26,
  "chapter_summary": "韦七娘在碧绿石屋中找到王风与血奴，提及自己正在寻找魔王并因此落泪。魔王从韦七娘的眼瞳中现身，引领王风穿过石壁进入魔域奇浓嘉嘉普。王风目睹十万神魔、十三只血奴与血鹦鹉的壮观景象。血鹦鹉兑现承诺，以魔力重现魔王十万岁寿诞时十万神魔滴血化鹦鹉的场景，揭示了血鹦鹉的真正来历。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "韦大姐，血奴在这里！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "韦七娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你们怎会在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "这说来话长，你又怎会找来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "韦七娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我在上面厅堂的照壁看到有扇暗门打开，所以走进来一看究竟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "方才你去了什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "韦七娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "趁乱到处搜查一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "你到底搜查什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "韦七娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "一个人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "是不是不能让我知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "你不愿意说，我也不会强迫你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "韦七娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "魔王！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "text": "你说谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "韦七娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "魔王！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魔王……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魔王……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "魔王",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "朕知道你心中有很多问题无法解决。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "魔王",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你很想知道血鹦鹉的秘密？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "魔王",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你抱起血奴，跟我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "魔王",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你为什么不随朕进来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_mo_wang",
      "text": "这是一面墙壁。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "魔王",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "朕叫你进来，你只管进来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "王风！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "血鹦鹉？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "我们又见面了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "你是否还记得欠我两个愿望？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你的愿望是什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "我的第一个愿望是要知道你的秘密。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这就是我的秘密。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
